text: Boniface Oluoch Otieno (born 22 December 1986) is a Kenyan international footballer who plays for Gor Mahia, as a Goalkeeper. ==Career== Born in Nairobi, Oluoch has played club football for Tusker and Gor Mahia. He made his international debut for Kenya in 2010. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Kenyan footballers Category:Kenya international footballers Category:Tusker F.C. players Category:Gor Mahia F.C. players Category:Kenyan Premier League players Category:Sportspeople from Nairobi Category:Association football goalkeepers
